{"tid":702901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔上載朋友 「瀨屎」照。出賣朋友被批無品","createTime":"2018-06-15T09:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T04:34:17.000Z","uid":15711,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"796ca527344846feb05a9b1e83aae2f7fc8f2a34","tid":702901,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"去旅行最怕乘搭長途車時人有三急，附近沒有廁所又未能解決，可謂一大酷刑。有連登仔發文，指朋友在韓國食香辣菜式後感肚痛，故乘的士回酒店，期間聞到屎味，發現朋友「真係瀨咗屎」，引起網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n連登仔「直行轉左轉埋右」昨發文，指話與朋友一起食辣嘢，「佢一直話好肚痛，所以我地就返酒店，點知，我地聞到有屎味，就問佢，點知佢真係瀨咗屎。」該連登仔形容當時整個酒店大堂和走廊充滿屎味，指友人不懂英文，故不敢向當地餐廳借廁所。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民替失禁女子心痛，「人生地不熟點知邊到有廁所，好慘」、「肚疴起上來真係無辦法，當事人自己都唔想的」。<br />\n<br />\n亦有網民認為連登仔出賣朋友非常無品，「如果我係瀬屎嗰個女仔，知道樓主post相上來嘅話，夜晚等你訓咗之後，將條沾滿屎嘅底褲，塞落你個口。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源連結:<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1241562/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1241562%2F&d=YnwWlSBWHhr3D8QJ6eb0lARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9ae1fef9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1241562%2F&h=5fd5b99f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1241562/</a>"},{"pid":"a370be833f05cc614c9a535bcacf0c9a542281aa","tid":702901,"uid":82917,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"點解呢單野係咁上新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e5e026e534b026ee4163dcc53b9e91c29e4189","tid":702901,"uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"個條明明係連登婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仔佢老味咩"},{"pid":"56482d3ee083b44941e91d7f9e7166a97caca4ee","tid":702901,"uid":15711,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a370be833f05cc614c9a535bcacf0c9a542281aa","tid":702901,"uid":82917,"like